-- Schulz Calls for Greek Investment Program, Rheinische Post Says
-- B y   S t e f a n   N i c o l a
-- 2012-02-13T23:00:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-13/schulz-calls-for-greek-investment-program-rheinische-post-says.html
Greece  needs an investment program
to help the country grow while it cuts its debt, European
Parliament President  Martin Schulz  said in an interview with the
 Rheinische Post .  The program should provide a “sustainable investment and
growth initiative” to accompany austerity measures, Schulz told
told the newspaper. He suggested that European Union funds might
be used to produce solar energy or expand Greece’s
transportation infrastructure, the  Rheinische Post  reported.  Stefan Nicola in Berlin at +49-30-70010-6246 or
